    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>Fortunately for Cutcliffe, winning four games at Duke is an achievement. If the coach&rsquo;s team matches that total for the second consecutive year, it will have actually exceeded expectations.</p>
<p>If Duke somehow pulls off a berth to a bowl game, Cutcliffe will look like a genius, and everyone might see that the Tin Man had a brain all along.</p>

